<P>
Game Story 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA011694-0105 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 004503 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
January 16, 1994, Sunday, Southland Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part C; Page 1; Column 4; Sports Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
