 Five minutes after Cal State Fullerton lost again, 59-50, to Utah State, Coach 
Brad Holland could be heard screaming in the closed locker room. 
</P>
<P>
 Ten minutes passed. Twenty.The game officials emerged from their locker room, 
showered and packed. Still no Titans. 
</P>
<P>
 It wasn't until 25 minutes after the game ended that the Titans, 2-10 overall 
