</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Juaquin Hawkins scored a career-high 21 points as Long Beach State defeated 
San Jose State, 78-71, in the Big West Conference Saturday night. 
</P>
<P>
 Long Beach State, 8-3 overall and 3-1 in the Big West, also got 14 points from 
Terrence O'Kelley and 13 from Eric Brown as it defeated San Jose State for the 
fifth consecutive time. 
</P>
