remaining in the game. Long Beach answered with a 10-2 run, keyed by Tyrone 
Mays' three-point basket, that gave the 49ers a 56-50 lead with 8:11 to go. 
</P>
<P>
 The Spartans didn't get closer than four points thereafter. 
</P>
<P>
 Terry Cannon, San Jose State's leading scorer with a 17.5-point average 
