<TEXT>
<P>
 Melja Deal Completed: Hycor Biomedicals Inc. said Friday that it has completed 
its acquisition of a German diagnostic products company. 
</P>
<P>
 Hycor in Irvine, which makes medical products, said that it bought Melja 
Diagnostik, which sells allergy diagnostic products and other autoimmunity and 
infectious disease products to clinical laboratories in Germany.  
</P>
<P>
 Melja, which is based in Kassel, Germany, had sales of about $2.1 million in 
1992. Terms of the sale were not disclosed. 
</P>
