<DOCNO> LA011694-0215 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 004613 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
January 16, 1994, Sunday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
