<P>
SUICIDE VICTIM'S BODY FOUND OFF HUNTINGTON BEACH 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The body of a 26-year-old man was found floating just offshore Saturday, about 
a dozen blocks north of the city pier, authorities said. 
</P>
<P>
 The body of Harish Gupta of Irvine was discovered by a group of surfers when 
it floated near the shore at 17th Street about 2:45 p.m., Lt. Jeff Cope said. 
Gupta had been reported missing Jan. 7, when a suicide note was found in a 
