<DOCID> 004671 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
January 16, 1994, Sunday, Ventura West Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 7; Column 1 
