6, Davis 6, Gay 4, Palmer 9, Arch 11, Gill 4, Reed 9, Fowlkes 32, Johnson 27. 
</P>
<P>
 Loyola 74, Alemany 50 -- Moose Bailey scored 20 points and Toby Bailey added 
14 as the Cubs easily rolled to their sixth consecutive win in a Mission League 
game at home. 
</P>
<P>
