Kubasak 2, Engler 9. LOYOLA -- Woods 8, M. Bailey 20, Edwards 8, Randazzo 2, D. 
Farmer 2, Thomason 2, T. Bailey 14, Canady 6, Parker 10, Klein 2. 
</P>
