<HEADLINE>
<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 In our review of "A Frolic of His Own," two characters' names were misspelled: 
Oscar's family name is Crease; his mistress is Lily. 
</P>
</TEXT>
